<div class="page-wrapper">
    <h1 class="title">Enrollment Plans</h1>
    <h3 class="subtitle">Ready for a new approach?</h3>

    <p class="description">
        For enrollment plans, there are 2 steps: 
    </p>
    <p class="description">
        1. Fill out & sign the California Department of Social Services Community Care licensing forms. These include: 
    </p>
    <ul class="description">
        <li>Identification and emergency information 
            <a href="https://www.cdss.ca.gov/Portals/9/Additional-Resources/Forms-and-Brochures/2019/I-L/LIC700.pdf?ver=2019-10-24-143032-763">(LIC 700)</a></li>
        <li>Child's pre-admission of health history 
            <a href="https://www.cdss.ca.gov/Portals/9/FMUForms/I-L/LIC702.pdf?ver=2017-07-16-155553-713">(LIC 702)</a></li>
        <li>Consent for Emergency Medical Treatment 
            <a href="https://www.cdss.ca.gov/cdssweb/entres/forms/english/lic627.pdf">(LIC 627)</a></li>
        <li>Parent Notification Additional Children in Care 
            <a href="https://www.cdss.ca.gov/cdssweb/entres/forms/English/LIC9150.pdf">(LIC 9150)</a></li>
        <li>Family Childcare Home Notification of Parents Rights 
            <a href="https://www.cdss.ca.gov/cdssweb/entres/forms/english/lic995a.pdf">(LIC 995A)</a></li>
        <li>Provide California School Immunization Record</li>
    </ul>
        
    <p class="description">
        2. Sign a contract & acknowledge a reciept of policies and procedures
    </p>

